The Stalkers Hunt Any Survivors | Final Pandemic | Full Post-Apocalyptic Survival Movie

*After The Pandemic* - Following a global airborne pandemic that wiped out 90% of the Earth's population, only the young and immune have endured as scavengers in a post-apocalyptic world. For Ellie and Quinn, the daily challenges to stay alive are compounded when they become hunted by the merciless STALKERS. Their perilous journey culminates with a sacrifice, death, and redemption.
2022.  Stars: Eve James, Kannon Smith, Juniper Preacher
